description: A collection of circles in the shape of a closed umbrella (a thin triangular shape with a hook-curved end on the right); there are also small triangular formations extending downwards from the main formation of circles. Each flavor circle has a different number in the center denoting how many lines stem from that point. There is a grayish-green triangle in the center of the formation and a darker grayish-green triangle on the right side on the hook-curved part.
